  lines:
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Excellent. So it all began on a Tuesday.
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Okay, so it was a pretty nice day. I think it was Tuesday. No, wait, maybe
      it was Wednesday. Actually no, it was Tuesday, because I remember I was thinking,
      \u201Cwow, Tuesday again.\u201D I don\u2019t know why I thought that. It just
      felt very Tuesday."
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: Anyway, I was just in the river, doing my own thing. I was not doing anything
      crazy. I was just floating there. Very peaceful. Very normal. The water was
      kind of cold, but not too cold. Like, not comfortable, but also not painful.
      Just water, you know.
  options:
